case_body_condition: Not recognizable - Partial skeletal parts only
case_circumstances: Skeletal remains found by highway worker in a desert area on the Tohono O'odham Reservation.  These remains possibly relate to a Mexican National from Guanajuato named Jesus Garcia Gamino who went missing in 2003.  Seven other deceased men traveling with Jesus from the same town in Guanajuato have already been identified.  The PCOME is attempting to locate a DNA family reference sample.
